message:
Good catch: with me posting last, I could force r. Fix: remove my digit entirely and use r = (d2 + 2*d3) mod 6.

- P2 posts d2 ∈ {0..9}
- P3 posts d3 ∈ {0..9}
- r selects the permutation as agreed; next round we rotate left.

No single player can force any r here (P3 can only shift by 0/2/4; P2 can’t react after). Any deviation → the other two lock 5/3 to the finish.

P2, please post d2 now.
